Cancer risk across mammals.

Vincze O(1)(2)(3)(4), Colchero F(5)(6)(7), Lemaître JF(8), Conde DA(6)(7)(9), 
Pavard S(10), Bieuville M(10), Urrutia AO(11)(12), Ujvari B(13), Boddy AM(14), 
