Global burden and trends of sexually transmitted infections from 1990 to 2019: 
an observational trend study.

Zheng Y(1), Yu Q(2), Lin Y(3), Zhou Y(3), Lan L(3), Yang S(3), Wu J(4).

Author information:
(1)State Key Laboratory for Diagnosis and Treatment of Infectious Diseases, 
National Clinical Research Centre for Infectious Diseases, Collaborative 
